      <div class="msgContentFrame">This was an extremely interesting read.  Personally, I use more of a light slash/WS build but I can definitely see the merit in this.  The one problem I could foresee is that using nothing but WS will kill a mob in a lot less hits and give out less total sp I believe.  I tend to spam Light Slash more as I've noticed that I get consistently more SP per mob by hitting as many times as possible. <br /> <br />In a group though, this sounds like a really great tanking style.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://somethingwitty.mmoguildsites.com" rel="external nofollow" title="somethingwitty.mmoguildsites.com">Something Witty- FFXIV linkshell</a></div></div>
